product.name: Universes Beyond: Assassin's Creed - Beyond Booster Display
product.cleanName: Universes Beyond Assassins Creed Beyond Booster Display

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Assassin's Creed® emerges from the shadows to join Magic: The Gathering! Your community will freerun through ancient locales with their favorite Assassins and take a leap of faith—the past is theirs to explore.
Beyond Boosters give your players a curated experience with every pack: they'll find classic characters, items, and moments from their favorite Universes Beyond stories inside. A full display gives your players the opportunity to dive headfirst into the set.
Contents:
• 24 Magic: The Gathering®—Assassin's Creed® Beyond Boosters
• 7 Magic: The Gathering cards
• 1-4 card(s) of rarity Rare or higher
• 3-5 Uncommon cards
• 0-1 Land cards
• Traditional Foil Showcase Mythic Rare card in <1% of boosters

Assassin's Creed® emerges from the shadows to join Magic: The Gathering! Your community will freerun through ancient locales with their favorite Assassins and take a leap of faith—the past is theirs to explore.
A Bundle is a great gift for Magic superfans visiting your store. They contain a little bit of everything to get a player's collection off the ground, plus an oversized Spindown life counter themed after the set.
Contents:
• 9 Magic: The Gathering®—Assassin's Creed® Beyond Boosters
• 7 Magic: The Gathering cards per Beyond Booster
• 20 Traditional Foil basic lands
• 20 nonfoil basic lands
• 1 Spindown life counter
• 2 reference cards

product.name: Universes Beyond: Assassin's Creed - Starter Kit
product.cleanName: Universes Beyond Assassins Creed Starter Kit

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Assassin's Creed® emerges from the shadows to join Magic: The Gathering! Your community will freerun through ancient locales with their favorite Assassins and take a leap of faith—the past is theirs to explore.
Starter Kits contain everything your players need for their first game of Magic. Learn the essentials or teach friends and family with the included Play Guide booklet, then enter the fray with two pre-built 60-card decks. After the fun, the decks can be tucked safely in the included deck boxes.
Contents:
• 2 ready-to-play 60-card decks: 1 red-white deck and 1 blue-black deck
• 2 Mythic Rare cards (1 per deck)
• 8 Rare cards (4 per deck)
• 2 deck boxes (1 per deck)
• 1 Magic: The Gathering play guide
